Package: chronotools
Title: Visualize and Plot Chronograms with R and phytools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Sergio", "Vargas", email = "sergio.vargas@lmu.de", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: The package chronotools is a hack of phytools that provides new functions and utilities to visualize chronograms in different ways and plot publication ready time trees.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1), phytools, plotrix
License: GPL (>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
